@subject: [obs <%= @e['type']%>-request <%= @e['id']%>] <%= @e['targetproject']%>/<%= @e['targetpackage']%>: created by <%= @e['who'%>
<% if @e['sourceproject']-%>
   <%= @e['sourceproject']%>/<%= @e['sourcepackage']%> -> <%= @e['targetproject']%>/<%= @e['targetpackage']%>
<%-else-%>
   <%= @e['targetproject']%>/<%= @e['targetpackage']%>
<%-end-%>

   https://build.opensuse.org/request/show/<%= @e['id']%>
<% if @e['description']-%>
   Description: <%= @e['description']%><%-end-%>
<%= @e['reqdiff']%>

To REVIEW against the previous version:
   osc request show --diff <%= @e['id']%>

To ACCEPT the request:
   osc request accept <%= @e['id']%> --message="reviewed ok."
   
To DECLINE the request:
   osc request decline <%= @e['id']%> --message="declined for reason xyz (see ... for background / policy / ...)."

To REVOKE the request:
   osc request revoke <%= @e['id']%> --message="retracted because ..., sorry / thx / see better version ..."
